		<p>Reading this article truly made me so happy. i am a firm believer of rick simpsons hemp oil remedy to help cure cancer. Although i cannot say the hemp oil cured my cancer by itself because i took it while getting chemo, radiation, and surgeries, but my doctors were most impressed on how fast my nodules shrunk.I just wanted to say that I was in the same situation as the women was in his article. I had stage 4 undifferentiated small round blue cell sarcoma which was also a 25% survival rate over 5 years. I was 20 years old when I was diagnosed in July of 2010. The short story of what I went through was initial tumor was on my hip which quickly metastizied to my lungs and later onto my brain which caused stroke symptoms to my entire left side. Chemo, radiation, and three surgeries later I was clear of cancer. I have now been in remission a few months less than 2 years. Hemp oil should be considered by every cancer patient in my opinion because it could only help. What is messed up is the government has known about the good benefits of the wonderfull hemp plant but keep it under wraps when it could be helping save lives!! Just figured I&#8217;d share my story and give my opinion on the matter. </p>
